  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Facilitating the distribution of household renewable energy technologies in Peru</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To increase clean energy usage in the Loreto region, Peru and develop income opportunities for Peruvians via a scalable pilot of a micro-distribution model for renewable energy technologies, including market-leading British brands, using a trained network of community agents. This will help enable low income families to meet their energy needs.</narrative>
